  "description": "A vibrant nighttime scene featuring a spectacular fireworks display over a large body of water. A prominent bridge, illuminated with rows of lights, spans the water and leads towards a cityscape in the background. The fireworks explode in a complex pattern of white and golden trails, resembling a burst of energy in the night sky. The cityscape consists of various high-rise buildings, also lit up, creating a dazzling backdrop. Dark, silhouetted hills or landmasses are visible between the bridge and the city. The water is dark and reflective, mirroring some of the lights above.",
